(9, 'Jay-Z and Beyoncé Purchase the Most Expensive Home in California History', '\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3.5k\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nScoop Harrison\r\nFri, May 19, 2023 at 7:25 PM GMT+2\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nThe post&nbsp;Jay-Z and Beyonc&eacute; Purchase the Most Expensive Home in California History&nbsp;appeared first on&nbsp;Consequence.\r\nOnce&nbsp;Beyonc&eacute;&nbsp;concludes her&nbsp;&ldquo;Renaissance World Tour,&rdquo;&nbsp;she&rsquo;ll have a brand new home to return to &mdash; and a very luxurious one at that.\r\nAccording to&nbsp;TMZ, Beyonc&eacute; and&nbsp;JAY-Z&nbsp;have purchased a 30,000-square foot home in Malibu for a record-breaking price tag of $200 million. Apparently that&rsquo;s the biggest real estate transaction in California history, smashing the previous record of $177 million. It&rsquo;s also the second most expensive home real estate deal in US history &mdash; behind only a $238 million transaction for a property in New York City.\r\nIncredibly, Beyonc&eacute; and JAY-Z actually got something of a deal, as the property was originally listed for $295 million. But with a combined net worth of $2.5 billion, the power couple likely had no problem securing a mortgage.\r\n\r\n- ADVERTISEMENT -\r\n\r\n\r\nThe home was designed by Japanese architect Tadao Ando. Art collector William Bell, its previous owner, spent 15 years building the all-concrete structure. It sits on an 8-acre property overlooking Malibu&rsquo;s Paradise Cove. You can see photos of the property below.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu House (1/5)\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu house\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu House (2/5)\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu house\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu house (3/5)\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu house\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu House (1/5)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu House (2/5)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyoncé and JAY-Z\'s Malibu house (3/5)\r\n\r\nJay-Z and Beyonc&eacute; Purchase the Most Expensive Home in California HistoryScoop Harrison\r\nPopular Posts\r\n\r\n\r\nTaylor Swift Calls Out Security Guard During Philadelphia Show\r\n\r\n\r\nLil Wayne Ends Show Early Due to Lackluster Crowd Response\r\n\r\n\r\nJay-Z and Beyonc&eacute; Purchase the Most Expensive Home in California History\r\n\r\n\r\nPost Malone Helped a Fan Buy a Home After Meeting at a Bar\r\n\r\n\r\nRobert Fripp and Toyah\'s 10 Best \"Sunday Lunch\" Performances\r\n\r\n\r\nBilly Corgan on Kurt Cobain\'s Death: \"I Cried Because I Lost My Greatest Opponent\"\r\n\r\n\r\nSubscribe to Consequence&rsquo;s email digest and get the latest breaking news in music, film, and television, tour updates, access to exclusive giveaways, and more straight to your inbox.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\nView comments\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nRead next\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z buy most expensive home ever in California: See the $200M property\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n1.6k\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTaryn Ryder&nbsp;and&nbsp;Kaitlin Reilly\r\nSat, May 20, 2023 at 6:23 PM GMT+2\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase new Malibu mansion for $200 million. (Photo: Backgrid, Getty Images)\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z just set a record with their $200 million mega mansion purchase in Malibu. It\'s the most expensive home ever sold in California and second most expensive real estate deal in the country,&nbsp;TMZ&nbsp;reports.\r\nThe 8-acre concrete compound overlooks the Pacific Ocean in the exclusive Paradise Cove area and was designed by famed Japanese architect, Tadao Ando. The 40,000 square foot home doubles as an art museum as the property was commissioned by modern art collectors Bill and Maria Bell more than a decade ago. It\'s no surprise, then, that the superstars took to the estate as their private art collection is said to be quite impressive.\r\nThe Malibu project took almost 15 years to build. According to&nbsp;Morley Construction Co., the project\'s contractor, design qualities include a water feature and a pool while utilizing 7,645 cubic yards of concrete.\r\nIf you can believe it, Jay-Z and Beyonc&eacute; got somewhat of a deal on the estate as the property was quietly listed for $295 million, per TMZ.\r\nLet\'s take a look inside.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z\'s new abode looks out onto the Pacific ocean. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nBeyonc&eacute; and Jay-Z purchase $200 Malibu mansion. (Photo: Backgrid)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n\r\nView comments\r\n\r\n\