com/entertainment/articles/2701827/michelle-williams-busy-philipps-critics-choice-awards-photos/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-ylk=\"slk:iconic BFF duos hit the red carpet together;elm:context_link;itc:0\" data-rapid_p=\"16\" data-v9y=\"1\">iconic BFF duos hit the red carpet together</a>, moms with their sons, and even kids of famous celebs pose alongside their parents &mdash; the latter has to be our personal favorite. For the 2023 BAFTA TV Awards, Kate Winslet&rsquo;s date was a very special person in her life, and the photos of the two had us doing a double take.</p>\r\n<p>The Oscar winner brought&nbsp;<a class=\"link \" href=\"https://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/2678764/kate-winslet-daughter-mia-body-positivity/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-ylk=\"slk:her 22-year-old daughter;elm:context_link;itc:0\" data-rapid_p=\"17\" data-v9y=\"1\">her 22-year-old daughter</a>, Mia Threapleton, to the awards ceremony and the two were practically twinning on the red carpet. Winslet and Mia had their hair styled in&nbsp;<a class=\"link \" href=\"https://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/slideshow/9423/celebrity-mom-daughter-kids-who-look-alike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-ylk=\"slk:a look that was almost identical;elm:context_link;itc:0\" data-rapid_p=\"18\" data-v9y=\"1\">a look that was almost identical</a>, and both sported some fabulous black ensembles &mdash; Mia wore a black and white jumpsuit while her mom wore a black cocktail dress. The two looked absolutely flawless.</p>\r\n<p><strong>More from SheKnows</strong></p>\r\n<ul class=\"caas-list caas-list-bullet\">\r\n<li>\r\n<p><a class=\"link \" href=\"https://www.sheknows.com/living/articles/2771733/loreal-voluminous-million-lashes-mascara/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-ylk=\"slk:Kate Winslet\'s Go-To Mascara Is a $10 Collagen-Infused Favorite That Shoppers Call the \'Best\' for Blonde Lashes;elm:context_link;itc:0\" data-rapid_p=\"19\" data-v9y=\"1\">Kate Winslet\'s Go-To Mascara Is a $10 Collagen-Infused Favorite That Shoppers Call the \'Best\' for Blonde Lashes</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure class=\"caas-figure\">\r\n<div class=\"caas-figure-with-pb\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"caas-img-container portrait\"><img class=\"caas-img caas-lazy has-preview caas-loaded\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xv75AuC4kWspbRh6mXyvmQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTEwOTE7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sheknows_79/1cf703b4db253e18a960b6e370cecf0c\" alt=\"Mia Threapleton and Kate Winslet attend the 2023 BAFTA Television Awards on May 14, 2023 [Photo by Joe Maher/Getty Images]\" width=\"534\" height=\"826\" loading=\"lazy\" data-caas-lazy-loading-init=\"1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image\">\r\n<div class=\"caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"caption-collapse\" data-id=\"m-0\">Mia Threapleton and Kate Winslet attend the 2023 BAFTA Television Awards on May 14, 2023 [Photo by Joe Maher/Getty Images]</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>While posing for some photos, the two even shared a very sweet candid moment. The below photo captured Winslet and Mia having a giggle, Winslet&rsquo;s arm wrapped around her daughter&rsquo;s shoulder. Mia, whom Winslet shares with former husband Jim Threapleton, was even on hand to watch her mom accept the BAFTA TV Award for Best Leading Actress for her performance in&nbsp;<em>I Am Ruth</em>&nbsp;&mdash; which she just so happens to<a class=\"link \" href=\"https://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/slideshow/2481150/celebrity-parents-who-acted-with-their-kids/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-ylk=\"slk:star in alongside her daughter;elm:context_link;itc:0\" data-rapid_p=\"20\" data-v9y=\"0\">&nbsp;star in alongside her daughter</a>.</p>\r\n<figure class=\"caas-figure\">\r\n<div class=\"caas-figure-with-pb\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"caas-img-container portrait\"><img class=\"caas-img caas-lazy has-preview caas-loaded\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mJg_Ave6bVX_HFcd2HN2Qw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTEwOTE7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sheknows_79/e75d08d8131efdf9f979638373698fb5\" alt=\"Mia Threapleton and Kate Winslet attend the 2023 BAFTA Television Awards on May 14, 2023 [Photo by Joe Maher/Getty Images]\" width=\"522\" height=\"807\" loading=\"lazy\" data-caas-lazy-loading-init=\"1\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image\">\r\n<div class=\"caption-wrapper caption-aligned-with-image\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"caption-collapse\" data-id=\"m-1\">Mia Threapleton and Kate Winslet attend the 2023 BAFTA Television Awards on May 14, 2023 [Photo by Joe Maher/Getty Images]</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>&ldquo;We did this together kiddo,&rdquo; Winslet said during her acceptance speech. &ldquo;There were days when it was agony for [Threapleton] to dig as deeply as she did and it took my breath away.&rdquo; Ok, we&rsquo;re not crying, you&rsquo;re crying. We love that these two were able to share this incredible moment together. And we cannot wait to see them in front of the camera again soon.</p>\r\n<div class=\"caas-da\">\r\n<div id=\"sdaAdvText-INARTICLE\">- ADVERTISEMENT -</div>\r\n<div id=\"sb_rel_sda-INARTICLE\" class=\"darla\"><iframe id=\"sda-INARTICLE\" tabindex=\"-1\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/rq/darla/4-11-1/html/r-sf-flx.html\" frameborder=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a class=\"link \" href=\"https://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/2775395/kate-winslet-daughter-mia-threapleton-bafta-tv-awards-photos/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" data-ylk=\"slk:Click here to read the full article.;elm:context_link;itc:0\" data-rapid_p=\"21\" data-v9y=\"1\">Click here to read the full article.</a></p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Bef